wikibasemachineassisteddepicts: The name of the extension's entry in Special:SpecialPages
wikibasemachineassisteddepicts-summary: Description appearing on top of Special:WikibaseMachineAssistedDepicts.
wikibasemachineassisteddepicts-save: Text for button to save confirmed suggestions
wikibasemachineassisteddepicts-save-titl: Title for button to save confirmed suggestions
wikibasemachineassisteddepicts-more: Text for button to show more images
wikibasemachineassisteddepicts-more-titl: Title for button to show more images
wikibasemachineassisteddepicts-confirm-a: Text for button to confirm all suggestions for an image
Title for button to confirm all suggestions for an image
wikibasemachineassisteddepicts-reject-al: Text for button to reject all suggestions for an image
Title for button to reject all suggestions for an image
wikibasemachineassisteddepicts-reset: Text for button to reset all suggestions for an image
wikibasemachineassisteddepicts-reset-tit: Title for button to reset all suggestions for an image
wikibasemachineassisteddepicts-suggestio:
Title for button to confirm individual suggestion for an image. Parameters:
* $1 - Text of suggestion to confirm

Title for button to undo individual suggestion confirmation for an image. Parameters:
* $1 - Text of suggestion confirmation to undo

Title for button to reject individual suggestion for an image. Parameters:
* $1 - Text of suggestion to reject

Title for button to undo individual suggestion rejection for an image. Parameters:
* $1 - Text of suggestion rejection to undo
